reviews.title: Where’s the beef
reviews.text: Stopped in for a quick takeaway. The kebab was good but they gave us chicken. You would think beef would be the go to if you order a sandwich. Next time I’ll be very specific.

reviews.title: Very disappointing!
reviews.text:
Extremely disappointed!
I live a mile away. I have already ordered several times at this establishment.
I ordered a dorum tonight, I didn't recognize the boss, has he changed?
I'm right next door, yet everything was cold. Far too much raw material!
Usually very generous and especially hot... waiting for a return.

reviews.title: I strongly advise
reviews.text:
Best kebab in Épernay nothing to say perfect fast and very warm 
Meat house 
Homemade sauce a delight

reviews.title: Disappointed but I believe!
reviews.text: I had come to eat here once unannounced and had eaten an excellent bulgur. I came back hoping to taste this famous bulgur again and unfortunately I was extremely disappointed, it lacked love and application...

reviews.title: Lovely kebab
reviews.text:
Good service, delicious food. Clean and delicate premises. 
Here the whole family can enjoy an affordable and tasty meal. 
Recommended!

reviews.title: Great!!
reviews.text:
Excellent! The waitress is very friendly and pleasant.
Speed and efficiency!
In addition, the quality is there and it is worth the price.
I highly recommend it!

reviews.title: 💀💀💀
reviews.text: malicious staff who scam. Please wake up and stop this. I paid €13 for two menus and only got one fries out of two. And no drinks are unacceptable!!!!

reviews.title: HORRIBLE
reviews.text:
I STRONGLY advise against this kebab. We paid for two menus and only got one fries out of two. And 0 drinks is a shame!! And also please review your onions.. and then the kindness of the staff should be reviewed.
You're trying to scam college kids biggggg shame on you.

reviews.title: Disgusting
reviews.text:
I find this unacceptable they made us pay more even though we should have had two menus when we had one the salad and the onions smelled of dishwashing liquid there were only three fries in the dish I do not recommend
Then he also asks us what we want to withdraw but he even leaves us to withdraw it

reviews.title: YUCK!!
reviews.text: We paid 13€ for two menus of 6.50€. We only had a menu with fries even though fries are included. And on top of that the onions tasted like plastic.

reviews.title: INADMISSIBLE!!! Really way too expensive
reviews.text:
The kebabs are really way too expensive, 30th for a kebab delivered, would you pay 30th for a kebab?
The prices are unacceptable!!

reviews.title: In “glass” and against everyone!
reviews.text: Very good kebab, but the friendliness of the waitress is not there at all! I asked for a drink and was told that I should have taken a menu!!

reviews.title: The best of Épernay!
reviews.text: The Bosphore deserves its reputation as the best kebab in Épernay, I recommend 100%! The others are far behind without a doubt!

reviews.title: A quite interesting place
reviews.text: We went in a late evening. We were very surprised when we tried the food that we had to go. We arrived at our hotel room and we enjoyed with a bottle of Champagne. I would say it was one of the best mediterrranean food that we ever had.

reviews.title: Excellent value for money
reviews.text: Food freshly prepared. Delicious gyros. Big portions. Really good value for money. Friendly and helpful staff. Highly recommended

They say two is better than one—and in Ixtapa-Zihuatanejo, that couldn’t be more true. Together, they deliver a travel experience that’s as diverse as it is authentic—earning Ixtapa-Zihuatanejo its place among Mexico’s top beach destinations.

reviews.title: Best kebab in France
reviews.text:
If you fancy a kebab with your chapagne, then this is the place to visit.
I would recommend this place all day long.

reviews.title: Good kebab
reviews.text: Visited this with my friends on a Sunday, good fast-food place and the kebab is really good. Good service also. Really liked their paprika-mayonnaise - hot and spicy!

reviews.title: Best Kebabs in France
reviews.text:
Best kebabs in the world, Been on holiday in Epernay many times over the past 10 years, and this is the best kebab house in the world.
The queues means that the kebabs are fantastic.

review.title: Kebab servi tiede en meme pas 30 secondes
review.text:
Patrone peu serviable, pas souriante
Admet que sa carte est trompeuse.. Avec kebab junior en 1er .. Alors on croit que c'est le prix pour un kebab " Normal"
Service très rapide à peine assis déjà le kebab mais viande tiède... C'est du réchauffer.. Pour 5€..
J'ai vu meilleur pour moins cher
Je suis d'avis entre 2 et 3 étoiles
